home.title: Aiga
home.descriptionA: Aafiaga atoa-Stack Polokalama Engineer ma le Upega Tafaʻilagi ma se Talaʻaga o Aʻoaʻoga Faʻamaoniga, mai le fausiaina o le Juvad Seambogies.
home.descriptionB: Additionally, I am a geography content creator who has successfully leveraged the algorithms of multiple social media platforms, including Instagram, YouTube, and TikTok, to gain a respectable and engaging follower base.

personal_summary.title: Aotelega Faatasi
personal_summary.text: A o le poto masani na matua faʻatulagaina polokalame o tagata atiaʻeina i Andlando, FL, na ou faʻaalia tomai i le tele o tekinolosi, mai ia Java ma le BED.JS. Faatasi ai ma se faʻasologa o galuega faʻaseʻe, e aofia ai le atinaʻeina o le Java Forwasication Program mo se upega tafailagi ma se upega tafailagi mo loli avetaavale, o aʻu o le au taʻavale ma fou. O laʻu tautinoga i le lelei tele, e iloa i loʻu mafai ona maua ai ni faʻafitauli o le poloketi, ia maua ai le manuia o le tagata faʻaaogaina.

entries.text: Faatasi ai ma tomai i HTML, CSS, ma Javascript Compuppers e pei o tali .Js, ou te faia le fiafia o le aufaʻatasi o le tagata faʻatau.

entries.title: Taaloga Atinaʻe
entries.text: Faʻaleleia o gagana pei o Java ma C ++, ou te faʻapitoa ai i lona fatuina siama poto masani poto masani poto masani masani, faʻamautinoaina o le faia o taʻaloga o le taʻaloga.

connect_four.title: Fesootai fa
connect_four.text: Ole tele o aiga o le sili atu i le 50+ faagaioiga o le fesoʻotaʻiga e fa taʻaloga. O lenei poloketi e aofia ai le faʻatinoina i luga o le 30 eseese o gagana gagana, e aofia ai Java, C ++, Python, JavaSon, ma isi mea. E le gata i lea, e aofia ai foi le 20+ eseʻese faʻavaʻa poʻo isi ituaiga, e aofia ai tali .Js, ruby ​​i luga o nofoaafi, asp.net, ma sili atu.

interop.title: Soifua Maloloina
interop.text: O se poloketi o pepa o loʻo faʻateleina i le va o gagana eseese. I lo o aofia ai ma le 15 eseese polokalame lautele ma 18 mamanuina o mamanu.

excel_scripts.title: Microsoft Excel Spredsheet Quets (vba)
excel_scripts.text: O se tusi aoga a vba tusitusiga mo Microsoft Excel. O lenei faletusi ua faʻaaogaina i galuega otometi i Excel Scientshests.

minecraft_json_generator.title: Minecraft Jsson Generator
minecraft_json_generator.text: O le moli moli JSON Bon Geontorator fausia i Python mo Minecraft Propment & Data afifi. O lenei poloketi e faʻaaogaina e gaosia ai ni faila JSON mo Misuraft Vs, e aofia ai mea masani, poloka, ma faʻalapotopotoga. Aoga tele mo le le gata i le faia o ni mea masani ai faʻamatalaga, ae mo mods o loʻo lelei e ala i le mola o loʻo ki ai foliga.

educational_experience.text: Ona o aʻu lava poloketi lava ia lava, ua ou mauaina foi le tele o tomai mai aʻoaʻoga. Kiliki ii e vaʻai i laʻu linkIn faʻamatalaga mo nisi faʻamatalaga.

portfolio_website.title: Patrick Worwin Portfolio Upega Tafaʻilagi
portfolio_website.text: O lenei 'upega tafaʻilagi o laʻu lava tuʻuga o laʻu tagata' upega tafaʻilagi, fausia ma tali .Js. O lenei poloketi e faʻaoga e faʻaalia ai oʻu tomai ma poloketi, faʻapea foi ma le tuʻuina atu o se tulaga mo tagata faigaluega e mafai ona faʻafesoʻotaʻi mai aʻu. O lenei poloketi e faʻaaoga e fausia ai se tagata tomai faʻapitoa i luga ole laiga.

lua_library.title: Patrick o le Loatrick Regic Library
lua_library.text: O se tusi lesona aoga a Lua Tusitusiga mo le lumanaʻi. O lenei faletusi e faʻaaogaina i galuega a le au taʻavale i Lua, lea e mafai ona maua mai mo galuega faʻapitoa-faʻatamala, pei o Lua e masani lava o loʻo vave tele ai le gagana.

neovim_config.title: Patrick's Neovim Conneg
neovim_config.text: O laʻu lava neovim o le faʻatulagaina. O lenei poloketi e faʻaoga e faʻatulaga ai Neovim e fiafia i ai, e aofia ai Key Coindbindings, autu, ma le pipi. O lenei poloketi e faʻaoga e fai ai Neovim sili atu tagata faʻaaoga-faauo ma lelei mo laʻu lava faʻaaogaina.

python_maps.title: Patrick's Faafanua Generator
python_maps.text: O le Iunaite Setete o Country County & State Demeve Breenrator, fausia ma Python faʻaaogaina le KaupandAs ma MaltPutlolib Faletusi. O lenei poloketi e faʻaoga e faʻatupu ai ni faʻafanua o le Iunaite Setete, e aofia ai Faʻafanua o le Setete ma le Malo. O lenei poloketi e faʻaaoga e faʻatupu ai ni faʻafanua a le suʻega mo le faʻailoaina o le ata ma le auiliiliga.

powershell_library.title: Patrick's Manbelshll FOLAFOLAGA FOLAFOLAGA
powershell_library.text: O se tusi aoga o tusitusiga o le mana o le mana mo le lumanaʻi. Aoga ma le $ talaaga faʻamatalaga tusitusiga, ou te mauaina lenei mea e aoga tele mo le otometi galuega mai le Windows Triends o le Windows OS.

ruby_library.text: O se tusi lesona aoga o Ruby tusitusiga mo le lumanaʻi. Aoga mo le lumanaʻi o ruby ​​i luga o le mamafa o le atinaʻeina o manatu.

pdf_builder.title: PDF tomai galue
pdf_builder.text: O se tagata masani PDF BDF na fausia ma Python e ala ile PDFKAIT ma Jinja2 faaopoopoga, faatasi ai ma HTTML ma JSON Pulea. O lenei poloketi e faʻaoga e maua ai faila PDF mai se lisi o tomai ma poloketi. O lenei poloketi e mafai ona faʻaogaina e fausia ai se masani PDF toe amata, e aoga tele mo galuega talosaga.

rijandel_encryption.title: Rijandel Nurcryption poloketi
rijandel_encryption.text: O se aiga o 10+ Faʻatinoga o le Rijandel Nucryption Algorithm i le 128, 192, ma le 256 pepa. O lenei poloketi e faʻaaogaina e faʻaalia ai le Rijandel Nurcryption Algorithm i le tele o polokalame faʻapitoa. O lenei poloketi e faʻaaoga e fai ai se aiga o le faʻatinoina o le Rijandel Nucryption Algorithm.

suprememc.text: A minecraft Mod e faʻaopopo mea fai pisinisi, ofutau, tagata ese, poloka, itu, ma tele isi foliga i le taʻaloga. Fausia ma Java Fualaau 8-15 mo le filifilia o Minecraft Faʻafeagaiga i le va o le 1.16 ma 1.20.
